"A storage category with specific limitations **must** be created first, "
"before it is applied to Before a storage category is applied to locations, "
"it must be configured with specific limitations in order to decide the "
"optimal storage location. Capacity can be limited by weight, product, and "
"package type."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:75
msgid ""
"To create a storage category, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
"Configuration --> Storage Categories`, and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Luo varastoluokka siirtymällä kohtaan :menuselection:`Varastointi-sovellus --"
"> Asetukset --> Varastoluokat` ja napsauttamalla :guilabel:`Uusi`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:78
msgid ""
"On the storage category form, type a name for the category in "
"the :guilabel:`Storage Category` field."
msgstr ""
"Kirjoita varastokategorian lomakkeella kategorian "
"nimi :guilabel:`Varastokategoria` -kenttään."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:82
msgid ""
"Weight limits can be combined with capacity by package or product (e.g. a "
"maximum of one hundred products with a total weight of two hundred "
"kilograms)."
msgstr ""
"Painorajoituksia voidaan yhdistää kapasiteettiin pakkauksen tai tuotteen "
"mukaan (esim. enintään sata tuotetta, joiden kokonaispaino on kaksisataa "
"kilogrammaa)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:85
msgid ""
"While it is possible to limit capacity by product and package type at the "
"same location, it may be more practical to store items in different amounts "
"across various locations, as shown in the :ref:`limit capacity by package "
"<inventory/routes/set-capacity-package>` example."
msgstr ""
"Vaikka kapasiteettia voidaan rajoittaa tuotteen ja pakkaustypin mukaan "
"samassa sijainnissa, voi olla käytännöllisempää varastoida tuotteita eri "
"määrinä eri sijainneissa, kuten :ref:`rajoita kapasiteettia pakkaustypin "
"mukaan <inventory/routes/set-capacity-package>` -esimerkissä esitetään."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:89
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Allow New Product` field defines when the location is "
"considered available to store a product:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salli uusi tuote` -kenttä määrittää, milloin sijaintia pidetään "
"käytettävissä tuotteen varastoimiseen:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:92
msgid ""
":guilabel:`If location is empty`: a product can be added there only if the "
"location is empty."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jos sijainti on tyhjä`: tuotteen voi lisätä sinne vain, jos "
"sijainti on tyhjä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`If products are the same`: a product can be added there only if "
"the same product is already there."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jos tuotteet ovat samat`: tuotteen voi lisätä sinne vain, jos "
"sama tuote on jo siellä."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow mixed products`: several different products can be stored "
"in this location at the same time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salli sekatuotteet`: useita eri tuotteita voidaan varastoida "
"tähän sijaintiin samanaikaisesti."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:99
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:164
msgid ""
"Odoo does **not** automatically split quantities across multiple storage "
"locations. If an incoming receipt contains several units or packages and the "
"first recommended location exceeds its capacity, Odoo still routes all items "
"to that same location instead of selecting another one with available space."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **ei** automaattisesti jaa määriä useisiin varastosijainteihin. Jos "
"saapuva vastaanotto sisältää useita yksiköitä tai pakkauksia ja ensimmäinen "
"suositeltu sijainti ylittää kapasiteettinsa, Odoo silti ohjaa kaikki "
"tuotteet samaan sijaintiin sen sijaan, että valitsisi toisen sijainnin, "
"jossa on vapaata tilaa."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:104
#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:169
msgid ""
"*(Example: If a location can hold 10 units and 12 units arrive, all 12 are "
"still assigned to that location.)*"
msgstr ""
"*(Esimerkki: Jos sijainti voi sisältää 10 yksikköä ja saapuu 12 yksikköä, "
"kaikki 12 osoitetaan silti kyseiseen sijaintiin.)*"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:108
