#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:137
msgid "Limit capacity by package type"
msgstr "Rajoita kapasiteettia pakkaustypin mukaan"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/daily_operations/storage_category.rst:139
msgid ""
"For companies using :doc:`packages <../../product_management/configure/"
"package>`, it becomes possible to ensure real-time storage capacity checks, "
