"Aktivoi :guilabel:`Toimitusliittimet`-osiossa :guilabel:`Starshipit-liitin`-"
"vaihtoehto."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:110
msgid ""
"After activating :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` page, click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
