"liittimen alla olevaa :guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping Methods`. Kun "
"olet :guilabel:`Toimitustavat`-sivulla, napsauta :guilabel:`Luo`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:115
